title: #92Noon! KimbreLL/Leber/Korzo
description: Perfect storm as Twins fans hear the team did not acquire touted reliever Craig Kimbrel, then watch the Twins bullpen surrender the lead in Cleveland last night. Ben Leber in studio midway through, then it's Korzo in for most of the final hour!
